{
  "text": "With respect to enabling factors, it appears plausible that these factors are not associated with frequent attendance in our study because most of the health care services are free of charge in Germany. Moreover, co-payments are quite low in Germany. However, an association between lower income and frequent attendance has been recently reported in a cross-sectional study [CITATION_1] . The differences between our study and the cross-sectional study could be explained by differences in the study design (cross-sectional vs. longitudinal study).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "2739329"
